archimate:Node.name: [SBB] NginX 1.x.x
archimate:Node.documentation:
Ontwikkelde webapplicaties - clients - worden door middel van NginX aangeboden.
NGINX is a free, open-source, high-performance HTTP server and reverse proxy, as well as an IMAP/POP3 proxy server.
SSL Offloading en loadbalancing in de DMZ gebeurt met NginX.
